SCOPE
-----
The CC BY 4.0 grant applies to the original material in this repository:
the extraction scripts (scripts/bls.py, scripts/bls_historical.py), the derived
tables and figures (outputs/), and any prose original to this repository
(e.g., README.md).

The underlying employment figures are published by the U.S. Bureau of Labor
Statistics (Occupational Projections and Worker Characteristics, Table 1.2)
and are in the public domain as a U.S. Government work. The CC BY grant does
not assert any new rights over that public-domain source data; it extends only
to the derived and original material listed above.

